@startuml
title <font size=10>Laporan Inventaris (Informasi Stok) - Owner</font>

actor Owner
participant View as "Login Page"
participant Controller as "LaporanController"
participant Database as "Database"
participant View2 as "Laporan Stok Page"

Owner -> Controller: Akses laporan inventaris\ndengan filter search & tanggal
Controller -> Database: Query semua barang\n(dengan search filter)
Database --> Controller: Return daftar barang
Controller -> Database: Query top 5 produk terlaris\n(join detail_transaksi & barang)\nJika ada tanggal filter,\nbatasi berdasarkan periode
Database --> Controller: Return top 5 produk\ndengan total terjual & revenue
Controller -> Controller: Untuk setiap barang:\n- Hitung total terjual\n- Hitung revenue (qty × harga_jual)\n- Include stok sekarang
Controller -> Controller: Aggregate data:\n- Total produk\n- Total revenue periode
Controller -> View2: Pass data: barangsWithRevenue,\ntop5Products, totalProduk,\ntotalRevenuePeriode, periodLabel
View2 --> Owner: Tampilkan tabel inventaris,\ntop 5 produk terlaris,\ndan summary box

@enduml
